---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SlideUp from "../components/SlideUp.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
    <section>
        <SlideUp tag="h1" parts="A little bit about me" />
        <p>
            Hi! My name is Nate, and I code and design things for the web. I
            love building new things, exploring technologies, and using
            technology to solve problems. I'm passionate about making the web
            accessible for everyone.
        </p>

        <p>
            Professionally, I develop and maintain a WordPress theme and custom
            plugins for the College of Agricultural and Life Sciences at UW
            Madison. My daily work involves exploring new technologies (React,
            WordPress, and more) and developing intuitive web solutions for
            content editors. I also maintain a
            <a href="/projects/share-the-dream">
                custom-made website and registration system for a local
                nonprofit.
            </a>
        </p>
        <p style={{ marginBottom: "var(--spacing-40)" }}>
            Besides development, I love to hike, travel, and explore our
            beautiful planet. I have been to many of the state parks in the
            great state of Wisconsin, and dream of someday taking a road trip
            around the U.S. and exploring our national parks.
        </p>

        <Button href="/projects" variant="minimal" arrow={true}>
            See my projects
        </Button>
    </section>
</Layout>
